This directory contains the mCRL2 toolset.

See the file INSTALL for compilation and installation instructions.

At the moment Windows builds are only possible using the gcc/g++ compilers
provided by MinGW and Cygwin.

Send bug reports to <bug@mcrl2.org>. Please include the version number from
`mcrl22lps --version', and a complete, self-contained test case in each bug
report.

If you have questions about using the mCRL2 toolset which the documentation
does not answer, send mail to <info@mcrl2.org>.

